    "Figure 3 c and d illustrate how LLMs can be extremely relevant in engineering design workflows.",
    "In this case, two different queries with different level of details are prompted into the GAD UI.",
    "The first prompt (see Fig. 3c) provides all details and parameters needed for the design of a spur gear, while the second (refer to Fig.",
    "3d) simply requests the component without any engineering details.",
    "The results show that in both cases GAD can create the requested item."
